---
// index.astro
import '../styles/global.css';
---
<html lang="es" class="dark">
    <head>
        <meta charset="utf-8" />
        <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
        <meta name="generator" content={Astro.generator} />
        <title>FranMaxi | IA & Software Solutions</title>
    </head>
    <body class="bg-[#050505] text-white font-sans antialiased min-h-screen selection:bg-purple-500 selection:text-white relative overflow-x-hidden">

        <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-full max-w-3xl h-[500px] bg-purple-600/20 blur-[150px] rounded-full pointer-events-none"></div>

        <nav class="relative z-10 max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-6 flex justify-between items-center">
            <div class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tighter">
                Fran<span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-400 to-blue-500">Maxi</span>.dev
            </div>
            <div class="hidden md:flex gap-8 text-sm font-medium text-gray-400">
                <a href="#servicios" class="hover:text-white transition">Servicios</a>
<a href="#portfolio" class="hover:text-white transition">Agentes n8n</a>
<a href="#portfolio" class="hover:text-white transition">Portfolio</a>
            </div>
            <button class="bg-white text-black px-5 py-2.5 rounded-full text-sm font-bold hover:bg-gray-200 transition shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(255,255,255,0.1)]">
                Agendar Llamada
            </button>
        </nav>

        <main class="relative z-10 max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 pt-16 pb-32 text-center">
            
            <div class="inline-block mb-4 px-3 py-1 rounded-full border border-purple-500/30 bg-purple-500/10 text-purple-300 text-xs font-semibold tracking-wide backdrop-blur-sm">
                NUEVA ERA DIGITAL 2026
            </div>

            <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-extrabold tracking-tight mb-6 leading-[1.1]">
                Sistemas inteligentes para <br class="hidden md:block"/> 
                <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-400 via-blue-400 to-blue-600">escalar tu negocio.</span>
            </h1>
            <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-400 mb-12 max-w-2xl mx-auto font-light">
                Combinamos desarrollo web de ultra velocidad (Astro) con automatizaciones avanzadas (n8n) e Inteligencia Artificial.
            </p>

            <div class="relative bg-[#0a0a0a]/80 border border-gray-800 rounded-2xl shadow-2xl p-2 max-w-2xl mx-auto backdrop-blur-xl transition-all hover:border-gray-700 hover:shadow-purple-500/10 duration-500 text-left">
                
                <div class="flex items-center px-4 py-3 mb-2">
                    <div class="flex gap-2">
                        <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-red-500/80"></div>
                        <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-yellow-500/80"></div>
                        <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-green-500/80"></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mx-auto flex text-xs text-gray-500 font-medium tracking-wider items-center gap-2">
                        <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-green-500 animate-pulse"></span>
                        ASISTENTE IA ACTIVO
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="px-4 pb-4 flex flex-col gap-5">
                    <div class="flex gap-3 items-start">
                        <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-500 to-blue-600 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 font-bold text-xs shadow-lg">FM</div>
                        <div class="bg-gray-800/40 rounded-2xl rounded-tl-sm px-5 py-3.5 text-sm text-gray-200 border border-gray-700/50 leading-relaxed shadow-inner">
                            ¡Hola! Soy la IA de FranMaxi. ¿Qué tipo de solución estás buscando construir hoy?
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <form class="relative mt-2" onsubmit="event.preventDefault()">
                        <input
                            type="text"
                            placeholder="Ej: Necesito un bot que responda WhatsApps y guarde citas..."
                            class="w-full bg-[#111] border border-gray-700 rounded-xl pl-5 pr-36 py-4 text-sm text-white focus:outline-none focus:border-purple-500 focus:ring-1 focus:ring-purple-500 transition placeholder-gray-500 shadow-inner"
                        />
                        <button
                            type="submit"
                            class="absolute right-2 top-2 bottom-2 bg-white text-black hover:bg-gray-200 px-5 rounded-lg text-sm font-bold transition flex items-center gap-2 shadow-lg"
                        >
                            Generar <span class="text-base leading-none">✨</span>
                        </button>
                    </form>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="mt-24 pt-10 border-t border-gray-800/50 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
                <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mb-6 uppercase tracking-widest font-semibold">Tecnología de la infraestructura</p>
                <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-8 md:gap-12 opacity-50 grayscale hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-500">
                    <span class="text-lg font-bold tracking-tight text-white">Astro</span>
                    <span class="text-lg font-bold tracking-tight text-white">n8n</span>
                    <span class="text-lg font-bold tracking-tight text-white">Cloudflare</span>
                    <span class="text-lg font-bold tracking-tight text-white">Docker</span>
                    <span class="text-lg font-bold tracking-tight text-white">PocketBase</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            
        </main>
		<section class="relative z-10 max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-32 border-t border-gray-900">
            <div class="text-center mb-20">
                <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-6">
                    Soluciones de <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-400 to-blue-500">alta ingeniería</span>
                </h2>
                <p class="text-gray-400 text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto font-light">
                    No instalamos plugins. Construimos infraestructuras a medida para que tu empresa opere en piloto automático y escale sin límites.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
                
                <div class="bg-[#0a0a0a]/50 border border-gray-800 p-8 rounded-2xl hover:border-purple-500/50 hover:bg-[#111] transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 group backdrop-blur-sm">
                   <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-xl bg-purple-500/10 border border-purple-500/20 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform text-purple-400">
    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="w-7 h-7">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3.75 6A2.25 2.25 0 0 1 6 3.75h2.25A2.25 2.25 0 0 1 10.5 6v2.25a2.25 2.25 0 0 1-2.25 2.25H6a2.25 2.25 0 0 1-2.25-2.25V6ZM3.75 15.75A2.25 2.25 0 0 1 6 13.5h2.25a2.25 2.25 0 0 1 2.25 2.25V18a2.25 2.25 0 0 1-2.25 2.25H6A2.25 2.25 0 0 1 3.75 18v-2.25ZM13.5 6a2.25 2.25 0 0 1 2.25-2.25H18A2.25 2.25 0 0 1 20.25 6v2.25A2.25 2.25 0 0 1 18 10.5h-2.25a2.25 2.25 0 0 1-2.25-2.25V6ZM13.5 15.75a2.25 2.25 0 0 1 2.25-2.25H18a2.25 2.25 0 0 1 2.25 2.25V18A2.25 2.25 0 0 1 18 20.25h-2.25A2.25 2.25 0 0 1 13.5 18v-2.25Z" />
    </svg>
</div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-white">Automatización n8n</h3>
                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
                        Conectamos tu ecosistema (WhatsApp, CRMs, Emails). Diseñamos flujos de trabajo que eliminan tareas manuales y ahorran cientos de horas mensuales.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-[#0a0a0a]/50 border border-gray-800 p-8 rounded-2xl hover:border-blue-500/50 hover:bg-[#111] transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 group backdrop-blur-sm">
                    <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-xl bg-blue-500/10 border border-blue-500/20 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform text-blue-400">
    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="w-7 h-7">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9.813 15.904 9 18.75l-.813-2.846a4.5 4.5 0 0 0-3.09-3.09L2.25 12l2.846-.813a4.5 4.5 0 0 0 3.09-3.09L9 5.25l.813 2.846a4.5 4.5 0 0 0 3.09 3.09L15.75 12l-2.846.813a4.5 4.5 0 0 0-3.09 3.09ZM18.259 8.715 18 9.75l-.259-1.035a3.375 3.375 0 0 0-2.455-2.456L14.25 6l1.036-.259a3.375 3.375 0 0 0 2.455-2.456L18 2.25l.259 1.035a3.375 3.375 0 0 0 2.456 2.456L21.75 6l-1.035.259a3.375 3.375 0 0 0-2.456 2.456ZM16.894 20.567 16.5 21.75l-.394-1.183a2.25 2.25 0 0 0-1.423-1.423L13.5 18.75l1.183-.394a2.25 2.25 0 0 0 1.423-1.423l.394-1.183.394 1.183a2.25 2.25 0 0 0 1.423 1.423l1.183.394-1.183.394a2.25 2.25 0 0 0-1.423 1.423Z" />
    </svg>
</div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-white">Agentes de IA</h3>
                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
                        Desarrollo de asistentes virtuales con memoria y contexto. Modelos entrenados con los datos de tu empresa para atención al cliente o uso interno.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-[#0a0a0a]/50 border border-gray-800 p-8 rounded-2xl hover:border-gray-500/50 hover:bg-[#111] transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 group backdrop-blur-sm">
                    <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-xl bg-gray-500/10 border border-gray-500/20 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform text-gray-400">
    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="w-7 h-7">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5.25 14.25h13.5m-13.5 0a3 3 0 0 1-3-3m3 3a3 3 0 1 0 0 6h13.5a3 3 0 1 0 0-6m-16.5-3a3 3 0 0 1 3-3h13.5a3 3 0 0 1 3 3m-19.5 0a4.5 4.5 0 0 1 .9-2.7L5.737 5.1a3.375 3.375 0 0 1 2.7-1.35h7.126c1.062 0 2.062.5 2.7 1.35l2.587 3.45a4.5 4.5 0 0 1 .9 2.7m0 0a3 3 0 0 1-3 3m0 3h.008v.008h-.008v-.008Zm0-6h.008v.008h-.008v-.008Zm-3 6h.008v.008h-.008v-.008Zm0-6h.008v.008h-.008v-.008Z" />
    </svg>
</div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-white">Arquitectura Web Edge</h3>
                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
                        Sitios web estáticos hiper-rápidos con Astro y despliegue global en Cloudflare. Seguridad militar y tiempos de carga de milisegundos.
                    </p>
                </div>

            </div>
        </section>
<section id="portfolio" class="relative z-10 max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-32 border-t border-gray-900">
            <div class="text-center mb-16">
                <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-6">
                    Sistemas en <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-400 to-emerald-400">producción</span>
                </h2>
                <p class="text-gray-400 text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto font-light">
                    Casos reales donde nuestra infraestructura automatizada multiplicó la eficiencia operativa.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
                
                <div class="group relative rounded-3xl border border-gray-800 bg-[#0a0a0a]/50 p-8 hover:bg-[#111] transition-colors overflow-hidden">
                    <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-32 h-32 bg-purple-500/10 rounded-full blur-3xl group-hover:bg-purple-500/20 transition-all"></div>
                    <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-6 relative z-10">
                        <div class="flex gap-2">
                            <span class="px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold rounded-full bg-purple-500/10 text-purple-400 border border-purple-500/20">OpenAI</span>
                            <span class="px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold rounded-full bg-green-500/10 text-green-400 border border-green-500/20">WhatsApp</span>
                        </div>
                        <a href="#" class="text-gray-500 hover:text-white transition-colors" title="Ver proyecto">
                            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor" class="w-6 h-6"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 6H5.25A2.25 2.25 0 0 0 3 8.25v10.5A2.25 2.25 0 0 0 5.25 21h10.5A2.25 2.25 0 0 0 18 18.75V10.5m-10.5 6L21 3m0 0h-5.25M21 3v5.25" /></svg>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-3 relative z-10">Agente de Ventas Inmobiliario</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6 relative z-10">
                        Bot conversacional conectado al catálogo de propiedades. Califica leads 24/7, agenda visitas en el calendario y guarda los datos en el CRM automáticamente.
                    </p>
                    <div class="h-1 w-full bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-500 to-transparent rounded-full opacity-50 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity"></div>
                </div>

                <div class="group relative rounded-3xl border border-gray-800 bg-[#0a0a0a]/50 p-8 hover:bg-[#111] transition-colors overflow-hidden">
                    <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-32 h-32 bg-blue-500/10 rounded-full blur-3xl group-hover:bg-blue-500/20 transition-all"></div>
                    <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-6 relative z-10">
                        <div class="flex gap-2">
                            <span class="px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold rounded-full bg-orange-500/10 text-orange-400 border border-orange-500/20">n8n</span>
                            <span class="px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold rounded-full bg-blue-500/10 text-blue-400 border border-blue-500/20">APIs</span>
                        </div>
                        <a href="#" class="text-gray-500 hover:text-white transition-colors" title="Ver proyecto">
                            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor" class="w-6 h-6"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 6H5.25A2.25 2.25 0 0 0 3 8.25v10.5A2.25 2.25 0 0 0 5.25 21h10.5A2.25 2.25 0 0 0 18 18.75V10.5m-10.5 6L21 3m0 0h-5.25M21 3v5.25" /></svg>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-3 relative z-10">Onboarding Automático</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6 relative z-10">
                        Flujo de n8n que detecta un pago exitoso, crea la cuenta del usuario en la base de datos, envía el email de bienvenida y notifica al equipo por Slack.
                    </p>
                    <div class="h-1 w-full bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500 to-transparent rounded-full opacity-50 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity"></div>
                </div>

            </div>
        </section>
        <footer class="relative z-10 border-t border-gray-900 bg-gradient-to-b from-[#050505] to-[#000]">
            <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-24 text-center">
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8">¿Listo para evolucionar tu sistema?</h2>
                <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center items-center mb-16">
                    <a href="#" class="bg-white text-black px-8 py-3.5 rounded-full text-sm font-bold hover:bg-gray-200 transition shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(255,255,255,0.15)] w-full sm:w-auto">
                        Iniciar Proyecto
                    </a>
                    <a href="#" class="border border-gray-700 text-white px-8 py-3.5 rounded-full text-sm font-bold hover:bg-gray-800 transition w-full sm:w-auto">
                        Ver mi GitHub
                    </a>
                </div> 
                <p class="text-xs text-gray-600">
                    &copy; 2026 FranMaxi.dev. Infraestructura diseñada en Tucumán.
                </p>
            </div>
        </footer>
    </body>
</html>